<br>
Bind at the zoneline and have gate loaded.<br>
<br>
We sent one group in to kill the advisor and another to keep the path back to the zone clear.<br>
<br>
I stood on the ledge before the bridge leading into Mistmoor.  If you're looking at the entrance, turn left and go to the edge.  You should be able to see the four blood wolves down there.  The black dire will spawn in the middle.<br>
<br>
One the advisor is killed, get everyone back to the zoneline.<br>
<br>
From the ledge, cast on the dire (doesn't matter what, prolly wont stick).  Now click Gate.  He will hit you with a 500 or so point harm touch.  It wont interrupt your gate.  Hang around at the zone for a few seconds and he'll come jogging up all alone.<br>
<br>
Begin smackage!<br>
